{"tid":2515231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣東話Rap｜「南亞仔」Youtuber自小被欺凌提款被當打劫 寫廣東話Rap歌自白\b：土生土長不是空談","createTime":"2021-05-03T23:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T04:28:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"558dee347449946a738ad68754447ce0dea0b840","tid":2515231,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:26:08.000Z","msg":"因一副「南亞仔」的面孔，黃智偉（Zain）自小已被定型為異鄉人，「差仔/印度/南亞/三個名你是但隨便揀/反正/就算/點嗌/邊個名你眼中都係犯」他Rap着一字一句，寫成《南亞仔》一曲，盡訴自己在香港成長的經歷和內心掙扎，其實他只有一個卑微的願望：「我純粹想正常生活。」<br />\n<br />\nZain是YouTuber，頻道有逾73,000個訂閱，近年更成立本地街頭服飾品牌NOTFORME，把香港本土特色如霓虹燈、紅van等加入品牌設計中，有港人更因移民而特登找他買返幾件衫留念。不少人都是從《口不對心》系列影片認識他，片中他擺出一副厭世的樣子，大講流行文化以至社會議題，在鏡頭前讚美，字幕卻寫着真心話調侃，觀眾看到無不發笑。不時有人在YT留言指他「中文說得很準」、「比地道香港人更香港人」，事實上，Zain真的在香港土生土長，「我已接受了，因為怎樣說也是這樣，理解就理解，不理解也沒辦法。」<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210504/KJF2N6GSOBEULGRWBFMCSQJVEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210504%2FKJF2N6GSOBEULGRWBFMCSQJVEM%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=8eb46adb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210504%2FKJF2N6GSOBEULGRWBFMCSQJVEM%2F&h=f1b4efa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210504/KJF2N6GSOBEULGRWBFMCSQJVEM/</a>"},{"pid":"debf8eaaa9193ec8f56b56927f9ca2bf7cb43298","tid":2515231,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:29:11.000Z","msg":"UST南亞仔<br />\n我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4c5cc24e64830e471c3bf830f8ce9bada684e7","tid":2515231,"uid":147029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:29:30.000Z","msg":"佢之前係唔係做空少"},{"pid":"6ff21cebf47fd90a612ad02a205ec0366b23a24c","tid":2515231,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"debf8eaaa9193ec8f56b56927f9ca2bf7cb43298","tid":2515231,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:29:11.000Z","msg":"UST南亞仔<br />\n我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:39:51.000Z","msg":"Thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9057db77b8a01dd78d4c1a8aac19ac80466da0","tid":2515231,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:52:24.000Z","msg":"寫Rap：<br />\n<br />\n「yo~民主黨」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「yo~賣香港」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「yo~又系民主黨」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「yo~又再賣香港」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e1d8028b66f770df1c1fc99.jpg/FSHzYWz1BQROc5qvvkyH4xtIl0hu4Tv4P9y6Hz_cuh8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e1d8028b66f770df1c1fc99.jpg%2FFSHzYWz1BQROc5qvvkyH4xtIl0hu4Tv4P9y6Hz_cuh8&h=e064425b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3b0da8f64dcf63f039efd939a66d64cbba4d7ca","tid":2515231,"uid":74339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:06:53.000Z","msg":"//被同學取笑成日常，Zain至今仍歷歷在目，「說起印度，就會全場看着我笑，當知道地理課會講印度，我那天可能就會不上學。因為飲食習慣不一樣，帶飯我覺得拿出來吃會被取笑，我就索性不吃，或者躲在廁所吃。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i